00:01:03.363 --> 00:01:07.568
The only problem was
that Dan and I once dated,

00:01:07.701 --> 00:01:12.573
a fact Becca always hated!

00:01:12.706 --> 00:01:15.676
But then they
went to therapy.

00:01:15.742 --> 00:01:18.679
And now they are
so happ-y.

00:01:18.812 --> 00:01:24.218
So let's raise
a glass to the--

00:01:24.318 --> 00:01:26.787
This wedding is slammin'!

00:01:26.920 --> 00:01:28.989
Okay, you guys,
let's dance.

00:01:29.156 --> 00:01:30.123
She never sticks
the landing.

