who are still trying to find
the monster

00:01:43.971 --> 00:01:46.139
who killed their beautiful
daughter.

00:01:46.206 --> 00:01:49.142
Everyone wanted me to say
a couple words, just--

00:01:49.209 --> 00:01:53.280
Uh, I guess, uh, one of
Rebecca's friends

00:01:53.413 --> 00:01:56.316
