to a better place,

00:02:17.304 --> 00:02:22.209
and I already
miss her face.

00:02:22.342 --> 00:02:26.680
I'm sure whoever killed
her has gone far away.

00:02:26.813 --> 00:02:31.351
It would be best to stop
looking and start a new day.

00:02:31.518 --> 00:02:37.090
